source.name: NWS Integrated Hydrologic Automated Basin Boundary System
source.description: The NOHRSC provides and maintains the NWS Integrated Hydrologic Automated Basin Boundary System (IHABBS) GIS database to support river and flood forecasting throughout the nation. Basin boundary data sets and RFC boundaries are in the form of shapefiles that have been tarred and gzipped.
